              img(src='img/filehorse.png' height='33' alt='FileHorse')

    section#share
      .container
        h2.title How it works

        p Messenger for Desktop is just a wrapper for the official client messenger.com, so it does not have an interface of its now. It works exactly like Chrome does, but as a stand-alone app.

        a.button.filled(href='#download' data-scroll) Download Now

